        "text": "In a bowl, mix ground lamb or beef with minced garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper."
      },
      {
        "step": 3,
        "text": "Shape the mixture into long, thin kebabs."
      },
      {
        "step": 4,
        "text": "Wrap each kebab in a piece of lavash bread."
      },
      {
        "step": 5,
        "text": "Place the wrapped kebabs on a baking sheet and bake for 20-25 minutes."
      },
      {
        "step": 6,
        "text": "In a small pan, melt butter and mix with tomato sauce."
      },
      {
        "step": 7,
        "text": "Serve the kebabs with yogurt and tomato sauce."
      }
    ]
